::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000053: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502010601.json-->
::'''Xuxia:''' My friend, that starship you've got there, it's gorgeous. How about it? Fancy a new crew member?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not at the moment...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106003-->
:::'''Xuxia:''' Don't be so hasty. Standing before you is an S-ranked starskiff pilot, A-ranked damage assessment expert, B-ranked ship mechanic, S-Ranked chef, C-ranked IPC sales associate, and A-ranked jade abacus fixer: Xuxia!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} And you are?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106005-->
:::'''Xuxia:''' Heheh, you'll be shivering in your boots when I announce my accolades. Standing before you is an S-ranked starskiff pilot, A-ranked damage assessment expert, B-ranked ship mechanic, S-Ranked chef, C-ranked IPC sales associate, and A-ranked jade abacus fixer: Xuxia!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502010601_198-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502010601_198-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} We can't fit that many people in our ride...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106007-->
:::'''Xuxia:''' Wha-! It's all just one person! Xuxia! Me! Go ask around the cosmos! Everyone knows that "The Multifaceted" is me!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You'll have to ask the conductor about this.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106009-->
:::'''Xuxia:''' What? Aren't you in charge around here? It was rhetorical anyway. Fine, I'll think of something and ask that conductor of yours when an opportunity arises.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The Express welcomes passengers from any world.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106011-->
:::'''Xuxia:''' Passenger? Have you got nothing around here that I can do? Forget it then. I'm not interested in this starship of yours any longer.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502106012-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106012-->
::'''Xuxia:''' ...*sigh* I won't impose then. Come to think of it, I'm not in a rush to leave right now anyway.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502010601_207-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502010601_207-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you doing now?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502106014-->
::'''Xuxia:''' I'm taking a break, and waiting for a chance for a voyage while I'm at it.
::'''Xuxia:''' Xianzhou prohibits long-life species from dwelling beyond the ship. Something about ecological disasters, I'm not too sure either... So if you want to embark on a voyage, you need to find interstellar work.
::'''Xuxia:''' To reach that goal, I took plenty of professional qualification certifications. The vocations I just mentioned were some of many.
::'''Xuxia:''' I'll give you this: Something I found while traveling outside. Though, you must've seen plenty of these.
::'''Xuxia:''' *sigh* Before the next voyage, I'll be hanging around on the Xianzhou. You're welcome to chat anytime you want.
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000054: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502010604.json-->
