:{{DIcon|Talk}} The Ambrosial Arbor grew then stopped. It's a miracle.
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000130: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act90000130.json-->
::'''Xuxia:''' Having seen the tree, I'm not too impressed. Firstly, the place is heavily guarded, and people can't get too close to it. Secondly, there's nothing special about it.
::'''Xuxia:''' Have you been to the chromium forest in Pakhurik? Towering chromium pillars that resemble massive trees block out sunlight like the canopy of a real forest. That forest is a fantastic creation of nature, a true miracle of the world! Instead of some mysterious legacy of an Aeon!
::'''Xuxia:''' I strongly recommend that you take a trip there. It's definitely much more magnificent than the Ambrosial Arbor, and it isn't dangerous.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
